WEBVTT

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
â™ªThat dayâ™ª

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
â™ªNothing stays together foreverâ™ª

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
â™ªI've quit romanceâ™ª

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
â™ªWho hasn't failed againâ™ª

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
â™ªCrying in deathâ™ª

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
â™ªAnd in lifeâ™ª

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
â™ªEven nowâ™ª

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
â™ªWe keep learningâ™ª

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
â™ªIt's no surpriseâ™ª

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
â™ªBeing happy is so hardâ™ª

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
â™ªWeirdly, I became a role modelâ™ª

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
â™ªOn the day we met again, we said hiâ™ª

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
â™ªIt was a reminder,
a test, and a complaintâ™ª

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
â™ªWho can do anything without regretâ™ª

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
â™ªI am all rightâ™ª

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
â™ªMay you live in peaceâ™ª

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
â™ªLet the world roarâ™ª

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
â™ªSounds like a carnivalâ™ª

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
â™ªBeing alive is never dullâ™ª

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
â™ªHow wonderful to be freeâ™ª

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
â™ªI became even better without youâ™ª

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
â™ªNothing can be perfectâ™ª

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
â™ªWe bless each other in painâ™ª

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
â™ªWe nod and smileâ™ª

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
â™ªMay we both be wellâ™ª

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.321 --> 01:43.792
= Episode 4 =

01:44.592 --> 01:45.911
You're from Shanxi, right?

01:46.471 --> 01:46.671
Yes.

01:46.712 --> 01:50.352
- Have you been to Dayun County?
- My grandma was from Yunlai Village

01:50.551 --> 01:51.352
of Dayun County.

01:53.232 --> 01:54.031
Now, Dayun County

01:54.072 --> 01:55.072
has developed well.

01:57.232 --> 01:58.232
It's changed a lot.

01:58.832 --> 01:59.391
(Yunjiangli Commercial Street
Renovation Project Begins)

01:59.391 --> 02:00.111
(Hello, Mr. Shen.)

02:00.432 --> 02:01.632
(This is our representative)

02:01.792 --> 02:02.512
(Qiao Jianbin.)

02:03.512 --> 02:03.952
(Hello.)

02:07.792 --> 02:08.512
By the way,

02:10.072 --> 02:11.871
didn't you stay longer
on your business trip?

02:12.192 --> 02:12.632
No,

02:12.632 --> 02:13.671
I only cut the ribbon.

02:13.711 --> 02:14.671
It was a quick trip.

02:16.151 --> 02:18.151
Don't watch the news.
I want to watch cartoons.

02:19.072 --> 02:19.512
Dad,

02:19.952 --> 02:20.831
do you have time now?

02:21.232 --> 02:22.431
I want to talk about

02:22.551 --> 02:23.632
the old city renovation.

02:23.671 --> 02:24.431
Sure.

02:25.711 --> 02:26.391
Talk over there.

02:26.431 --> 02:26.991
Haochen.

02:28.792 --> 02:29.312
Haochen.

02:30.591 --> 02:32.151
I've told you many times

02:33.551 --> 02:34.551
it will damage your eyes.

02:43.151 --> 02:43.831
Qiao!

02:44.111 --> 02:44.752
Meal is ready!

02:46.032 --> 02:47.551
After I finish these two rollers,

02:47.591 --> 02:48.032
I'll come.

02:48.671 --> 02:52.632
- You are here, Yazhen.
- Ms. Sha, getting a perm?

02:52.752 --> 02:53.312
Yes.

02:54.312 --> 02:54.831
Yazhen,

02:55.312 --> 02:57.111
Qiao is quite popular now.

02:57.551 --> 02:58.752
On TV,

02:58.792 --> 03:00.151
he spoke so eloquently,

03:00.512 --> 03:02.352
even upstaging the county mayor!

03:02.711 --> 03:04.551
Of course.

03:05.192 --> 03:06.352
With all these stores around,

03:06.551 --> 03:08.271
they let me
be the merchant representative.

03:08.312 --> 03:09.632
I had to do my best.

03:09.711 --> 03:10.232
Right?

03:10.591 --> 03:12.391
No wonder you raised
such good daughters.

03:12.991 --> 03:14.512
The younger one

03:14.551 --> 03:15.192
is working now?

03:18.711 --> 03:19.671
What's the point?

03:20.632 --> 03:21.912
She never calls,

03:22.111 --> 03:23.391
and only sends a text

03:23.952 --> 03:24.991
during holidays.

03:25.391 --> 03:26.792
Lin is better.

03:27.111 --> 03:27.871
She stays

03:27.871 --> 03:28.912
with us.

03:29.271 --> 03:31.151
She is our sweet daughter.

03:32.632 --> 03:32.991
Right.

03:33.271 --> 03:34.032
Is Lin

03:34.072 --> 03:35.072
about to marry soon?

03:35.912 --> 03:36.632
Very soon.

03:37.591 --> 03:38.591
My future son-in-law

03:38.711 --> 03:40.671
is going to be a banker.

03:42.192 --> 03:42.792
Beauty.

03:43.271 --> 03:44.752
I work at Dayun County's

03:44.831 --> 03:46.352
largest fertilizer factory.

03:47.111 --> 03:49.711
I am responsible for holiday
group purchase benefits.

03:52.352 --> 03:53.352
Add me on WeChat.

03:53.591 --> 03:54.591
If I need to purchase,

03:54.591 --> 03:55.192
I'll tell you.

03:56.312 --> 03:57.032
Feel free to come

03:57.032 --> 03:58.151
to our counter.

03:58.711 --> 03:59.352
Take this.

04:01.871 --> 04:03.032
You are so rigid.

04:03.032 --> 04:04.431
How can you make money?

04:04.711 --> 04:06.831
Many salesgirls want my contact,

04:06.952 --> 04:07.871
yet they can't get it.

04:10.671 --> 04:12.072
Your hands are so fair.

04:13.151 --> 04:14.032
Are you insane?

04:15.072 --> 04:16.391
I'll pick you up after work.

04:18.151 --> 04:18.992
Are you insane?

04:19.952 --> 04:20.351
You!

04:20.391 --> 04:21.031
Stop there!

04:22.351 --> 04:23.271
Don't touch me.

04:23.911 --> 04:24.432
Honey.

04:25.112 --> 04:25.992
She hit me!

04:26.151 --> 04:27.192
Why did you hit him?

04:27.312 --> 04:28.231
Why did you hit me?

04:28.271 --> 04:29.391
You wretch!

04:29.432 --> 04:30.672
Are you insane?

04:30.711 --> 04:31.271
Let go of me!

04:31.271 --> 04:31.952
What's going on?

04:31.952 --> 04:32.552
Let go of me!

04:33.271 --> 04:33.791
Let go!

04:33.791 --> 04:34.831
I'll report you!

04:35.280 --> 04:41.904
(Police)

04:42.512 --> 04:42.952
Lin.

04:43.552 --> 04:43.872
Lin.

04:45.391 --> 04:47.231
We agreed to discuss
the wedding at my place.

04:54.432 --> 04:55.031
Dad. Mom.

04:55.271 --> 04:55.992
We're back.

05:01.231 --> 05:02.031
Troublemaker.

05:02.391 --> 05:03.271
How dare you come!

05:03.591 --> 05:04.072
Auntie. I...

05:04.072 --> 05:04.512
Lin.

05:09.632 --> 05:10.072
Dad.

05:11.312 --> 05:11.752
Here.

05:12.432 --> 05:13.151
Have some fruits.

05:17.711 --> 05:18.112
Dad.

05:18.512 --> 05:19.552
This is the money from you

05:19.632 --> 05:21.031
(Details of wedding costs)
and my mom for our marriage.

05:21.351 --> 05:23.072
Excluding the betrothal money
for Lin family,

05:23.312 --> 05:23.911
wedding rings,

05:24.112 --> 05:25.312
and other

05:25.351 --> 05:26.312
expenses,

05:26.552 --> 05:29.711
there is still 98,654 yuan.

05:30.192 --> 05:31.072
I'll ask one question.

05:31.672 --> 05:33.151
What about the cash gifts?

05:33.271 --> 05:35.351
You'll have it.
Lin and I agreed on this.

05:39.432 --> 05:40.591
Let me break it down.

05:42.031 --> 05:44.031
The wedding photos cost

05:44.151 --> 05:45.271
9,588 yuan.

05:45.872 --> 05:46.872
I chose a moderately

05:46.872 --> 05:48.112
priced wedding planner,

05:48.432 --> 05:49.432
costing 18,800 yuan.

05:50.151 --> 05:51.831
For accommodation
for out-of-town guests,

05:52.112 --> 05:53.271
I booked 20 standard rooms.

05:53.591 --> 05:55.552
Each room costs 288 yuan,

05:56.031 --> 05:57.992
totaling 5,760 yuan.

05:58.591 --> 05:59.552
About the return gifts,

05:59.791 --> 06:00.591
we'll prepare them.

06:01.351 --> 06:02.512
15,000 yuan should suffice.

06:02.872 --> 06:04.432
I booked 20 banquet tables.

06:04.632 --> 06:05.512
Each table costs

06:05.512 --> 06:06.672
1,288 yuan.

06:07.271 --> 06:08.231
20 tables?

06:08.271 --> 06:09.391
That's not enough.

06:10.151 --> 06:10.672
Mom.

06:11.112 --> 06:12.512
Our bank has rules.

06:12.831 --> 06:15.112
For weddings,
not more than 20 tables are allowed.

06:15.312 --> 06:15.992
No exceptions.

06:16.351 --> 06:17.591
Otherwise, my superior and I

06:17.591 --> 06:18.591
would be affected.

06:18.911 --> 06:20.391
Did your bank mention

06:20.831 --> 06:22.351
if your fiancee frequently visiting

06:22.391 --> 06:22.992
police stations

06:23.112 --> 06:24.192
would affect your career?

06:29.512 --> 06:29.791
Auntie.

06:29.791 --> 06:31.031
Get straight to the point.

06:31.151 --> 06:32.231
Stop being so sarcastic,

06:32.231 --> 06:32.711
okay?

06:33.952 --> 06:35.151
I'm being sarcastic?

06:35.432 --> 06:36.992
As a young woman,

06:37.351 --> 06:38.872
you always cause trouble.

06:39.752 --> 06:40.632
Why don't you

06:40.632 --> 06:41.872
think of the consequences?

06:42.231 --> 06:42.872
Do you live

06:42.872 --> 06:43.872
in the police station?

06:44.031 --> 06:45.711
You go there many times a month!

06:47.231 --> 06:47.791
Auntie.

06:48.031 --> 06:49.312
This wasn't my fault!

06:49.791 --> 06:50.672
Today, that man

06:50.672 --> 06:51.791
harassed me first.

06:51.992 --> 06:52.471
Enough!

06:54.031 --> 06:54.992
Be quiet.

06:57.112 --> 06:57.791
Qiao Lin.

06:58.351 --> 06:59.911
You're Lin Tao's fiancee.

07:00.872 --> 07:01.952
Our town is small.

07:02.432 --> 07:03.791
If you keep causing trouble

07:04.192 --> 07:05.151
and word gets out,

07:05.312 --> 07:06.831
it'll affect Tao's career.

07:07.112 --> 07:07.711
Understand?

07:08.151 --> 07:09.312
If his career gets affected,

07:09.711 --> 07:10.672
you'll be affected too.

07:10.992 --> 07:11.831
My son

07:12.112 --> 07:13.672
graduated from a top university

07:13.752 --> 07:14.872
with a master's degree.

07:15.271 --> 07:16.911
He's a bank client manager now,

07:17.072 --> 07:19.112
and will become a department head,

07:19.312 --> 07:21.072
branch manager, and even bank president!

07:21.351 --> 07:22.711
Look at you.

07:22.952 --> 07:24.391
You're ruining my son's

07:24.432 --> 07:25.552
bright future!

07:25.872 --> 07:26.831
We are to blame

07:26.911 --> 07:28.312
for accepting your marriage.

07:43.552 --> 07:47.911
Lin. I've calculated it.

07:48.151 --> 07:48.632
We still

07:48.632 --> 07:49.911
have 17,866 yuan.

07:50.151 --> 07:50.791
It's enough

07:50.831 --> 07:51.591
for our honeymoon.

07:52.952 --> 07:53.752
Enjoy it yourself.

07:55.952 --> 07:56.432
Lin.

08:12.632 --> 08:19.072
(- What're you doing?)
(- At work. What's wrong?)

08:24.872 --> 08:25.632
(Nothing.)

08:27.312 --> 08:28.471
(When will you come home?)

08:34.991 --> 08:35.432
Lin.

08:35.631 --> 08:36.272
Have an apple.

08:36.392 --> 08:37.471
Thanks, Dad.

08:50.511 --> 08:50.991
Dad.

08:52.792 --> 08:54.432
Have you used the betrothal money

08:54.432 --> 08:55.192
from Lin Tao?

08:55.751 --> 08:56.511
Yes.

08:56.991 --> 08:58.231
We agreed to use

08:58.591 --> 09:00.991
the money for renovating the new store.

09:02.312 --> 09:03.471
After we sell the old store,

09:03.511 --> 09:04.672
we'll return it to you.

09:05.432 --> 09:05.991
What now?

09:06.552 --> 09:07.511
Did Lin Tao's parents

09:07.552 --> 09:08.312
say anything?

09:08.792 --> 09:09.711
Not exactly.

09:09.711 --> 09:10.672
I'm Just asking.

09:12.471 --> 09:13.552
How's your wedding

09:13.792 --> 09:14.792
preparations going?

09:15.511 --> 09:16.631
He's been busy with work.

09:17.072 --> 09:18.591
I've been busy lately too.

09:29.831 --> 09:30.231
Right.

09:31.111 --> 09:32.672
I need to go on a business trip soon.

09:33.552 --> 09:34.912
A study trip

09:34.912 --> 09:35.672
in Jingzhou.

09:36.392 --> 09:37.111
To Jingzhou?

09:38.471 --> 09:39.272
How long?

09:39.711 --> 09:40.672
Have you told Lin Tao?

09:41.432 --> 09:41.831
Not yet.

09:42.111 --> 09:42.432
Wait.

09:42.831 --> 09:43.351
Lin.

09:43.432 --> 09:44.591
You should at least

09:44.631 --> 09:46.471
inform Lin Tao about the trip.

09:46.711 --> 09:48.552
Lin Tao is a key talent

09:48.552 --> 09:49.471
at the bank now.

09:49.471 --> 09:50.672
He has his pride.

09:51.032 --> 09:52.192
You need to get along well.

09:52.631 --> 09:53.231
Exactly.

09:53.312 --> 09:54.792
You're about to get married.

09:54.952 --> 09:55.991
You should be considerate.

09:56.072 --> 09:56.591
Understand?

09:56.792 --> 09:57.591
You should

09:57.591 --> 09:59.152
discuss everything with Lin Tao.

09:59.392 --> 10:00.032
You hear me?

10:00.392 --> 10:00.831
Yes.

10:01.231 --> 10:01.831
Right.

10:02.032 --> 10:03.192
You two should live

10:03.231 --> 10:04.432
a peaceful life together.

10:04.831 --> 10:05.672
Just stay

10:05.672 --> 10:07.032
with us.

10:07.672 --> 10:08.792
Don't be like your sister.

10:09.111 --> 10:09.711
This daughter

10:09.711 --> 10:10.711
is like she never exists.

10:19.248 --> 10:22.885
â™ªI'll make you adore me,
let the spotlight be mineâ™ª

10:22.885 --> 10:26.878
â™ªLike a raw diamond,
my presence shapes the worldâ™ª

10:26.878 --> 10:30.402
â™ªBlooming in my colors,
every frame's perfectionâ™ª

10:31.001 --> 10:35.737
â™ªMy beauty's defined by none
but my own commandâ™ª

10:37.040 --> 10:39.999
â™ªLet the spotlight be mineâ™ª

10:40.880 --> 10:44.304
â™ªLet the spotlight be mineâ™ª

10:44.304 --> 10:46.064
â™ªLet the spotlight be mineâ™ª

10:47.591 --> 10:49.432
The list and procedures
of the Family Feast

10:49.471 --> 10:50.591
need double-checking.

10:50.952 --> 10:52.312
Contact me immediately

10:52.511 --> 10:53.392
if you need me.

10:53.912 --> 10:54.351
Alright.

10:55.792 --> 10:56.152
Yan.

10:56.591 --> 10:57.152
We have

10:57.152 --> 10:58.032
a gathering tonight.

10:58.032 --> 10:58.672
Want to join us?

10:59.351 --> 11:00.312
I'll pass.

11:00.511 --> 11:01.432
My boyfriend will come.

11:01.792 --> 11:02.751
Boyfriend?

11:03.072 --> 11:04.272
He is your fiance, right?

11:05.152 --> 11:06.432
Go home early tonight, alright?

11:06.711 --> 11:07.111
Okay.

11:07.432 --> 11:08.991
Have a good date tonight.

11:09.072 --> 11:09.631
I'm leaving.

11:23.272 --> 11:23.751
Yan.

11:25.032 --> 11:25.711
Qiao Yan!

11:31.312 --> 11:33.792
I am so lucky today, meeting you
right after work.

11:33.871 --> 11:34.351
Otherwise,

11:34.392 --> 11:35.231
I couldn't find you.

11:41.831 --> 11:44.192
- Why are you here?
- I called off the wedding.

11:45.312 --> 11:47.032
I'm now free from all worries,

11:47.351 --> 11:48.711
so I thought to try my luck

11:48.912 --> 11:49.751
in a big city.

11:50.272 --> 11:51.351
I haven't found a place.

11:51.511 --> 11:52.432
Can I go to your place?

11:58.591 --> 11:59.552
There's a cafe opposite.

12:00.072 --> 12:00.831
Let's talk there.

12:02.072 --> 12:02.711
Alright.

12:02.831 --> 12:03.952
No need for cafe.

12:03.991 --> 12:04.552
What a waste.

12:04.631 --> 12:04.991
Let's go.

12:05.111 --> 12:05.751
We can talk

12:05.751 --> 12:07.111
in your place.

12:15.751 --> 12:16.312
Yan.

12:24.072 --> 12:24.831
Your boyfriend?

12:31.032 --> 12:32.152
My future brother-in-law?

12:32.192 --> 12:32.711
Hi.

12:35.392 --> 12:35.952
This is...

12:35.952 --> 12:36.231
I'm...

12:36.231 --> 12:36.912
My cousin.

12:37.831 --> 12:38.552
She came to me.

12:40.792 --> 12:41.392
Hello.

12:42.192 --> 12:43.672
I'm picking her up for dinner.

12:43.711 --> 12:44.511
Want to join us?

12:45.111 --> 12:46.111
She just arrived,

12:46.511 --> 12:47.272
and is a bit tired.

12:47.511 --> 12:48.272
I'll find a hotel

12:48.312 --> 12:49.072
to settle her in.

12:49.552 --> 12:49.912
Alright.

12:50.672 --> 12:51.032
Alright.

12:52.032 --> 12:53.991
We can only
go to the restaurant another day.

12:54.152 --> 12:54.552
Okay?

12:54.751 --> 12:54.991
Okay.

12:55.231 --> 12:56.072
Go home then.

12:57.032 --> 12:57.591
I'll call you

12:57.792 --> 12:58.871
when I get home.

13:02.751 --> 13:03.152
Go.

13:04.272 --> 13:04.991
Bye then.

13:06.591 --> 13:07.072
Be careful.

13:07.192 --> 13:07.991
Drive safely.

13:32.912 --> 13:35.552
The place is great
with convenient transportation.

13:36.511 --> 13:38.552
Qiao Yan. Why did you say
I'm your cousin?

13:39.111 --> 13:41.792
There's a refrigerator.
A convenience store is nearby.

13:42.831 --> 13:43.711
I can see it now.

13:44.032 --> 13:44.792
Your boyfriend

13:44.831 --> 13:45.672
is well-off,

13:45.751 --> 13:46.591
so you look down on

13:46.591 --> 13:47.511
me, a loser,

13:47.511 --> 13:47.912
right?

13:48.152 --> 13:48.871
Go back soon.

13:49.511 --> 13:50.591
What do you mean?

13:52.032 --> 13:53.231
You canceled the wedding,

13:53.392 --> 13:54.552
and didn't tell our parents.

13:55.272 --> 13:56.392
They'll search for you.

13:57.672 --> 13:57.991
Right.

13:58.432 --> 13:59.392
After I get settled,

13:59.432 --> 14:00.392
I'll tell them then.

14:00.432 --> 14:01.072
It's the same.

14:01.631 --> 14:02.751
Wait, get back to the point.

14:02.792 --> 14:03.392
I'm asking you

14:03.511 --> 14:04.991
why you didn't tell your boyfriend

14:05.072 --> 14:06.312
I'm your elder sister.

14:22.231 --> 14:24.111
Grandma and I share
a household registration.

14:24.631 --> 14:25.432
My surname is Xu,

14:26.351 --> 14:27.152
not Qiao.

14:28.032 --> 14:28.711
So,

14:28.751 --> 14:29.471
you should know

14:30.312 --> 14:31.072
my only family

14:31.351 --> 14:31.991
is Grandma.

14:34.272 --> 14:34.631
Right.

14:35.511 --> 14:36.552
I know you've never been

14:36.591 --> 14:37.751
close with our parents.

14:38.111 --> 14:39.111
But I never thought

14:39.192 --> 14:39.912
we weren't family.

14:39.952 --> 14:40.672
Only you think so.

14:49.072 --> 14:49.631
Qiao Lin.

14:50.072 --> 14:51.272
You came here

14:51.312 --> 14:52.111
without telling me.

14:53.231 --> 14:54.432
What I've done for you

14:55.952 --> 14:57.351
is already more than enough.

14:57.471 --> 14:58.312
Go home after running

14:58.511 --> 14:59.432
out of money.

14:59.912 --> 15:00.871
Don't make them worry.

15:03.072 --> 15:04.432
You can stay if you want,

15:07.111 --> 15:09.272
but I'm not obligated

15:09.312 --> 15:10.231
to take care of you.

15:12.231 --> 15:12.711
Qiao Yan.

15:12.952 --> 15:13.991
Had I known it,

15:14.032 --> 15:14.591
I would've

15:14.631 --> 15:15.432
never come to you.

15:15.432 --> 15:15.912
Understand?

15:21.751 --> 15:22.552
My surname is Xu.

15:23.392 --> 15:24.032
Xu Yan.

15:27.552 --> 15:29.032
You are Qiao Yan.

15:29.111 --> 15:30.272
You are Qiao Yan! Qiao...

15:44.880 --> 15:49.034
(Transfer to Qiao Lin)

15:51.312 --> 15:52.831
(The price of your heartlessness.)

16:21.751 --> 16:22.471
So heartless!

16:24.152 --> 16:25.792
I shouldn't have saved you back then!

16:31.192 --> 16:33.552
- Wild child!
- Wild child!

16:33.631 --> 16:34.792
Wild child.

16:34.871 --> 16:36.152
Wild child!

16:36.312 --> 16:37.312
- Wild child!
- Wild child!

16:37.351 --> 16:39.432
Move! Let me go home!

16:39.792 --> 16:42.591
Qiao Yan, unwanted one.

16:42.751 --> 16:45.351
Wild child, without parents!

16:48.672 --> 16:51.032
How dare you push me?

16:52.152 --> 16:53.552
None of your business!

16:54.672 --> 16:56.032
Who dares bully my sister?

16:57.591 --> 16:58.312
Do you dare?

16:58.912 --> 17:00.511
- No.
- No.

17:05.152 --> 17:06.432
You're my sister now.

17:11.592 --> 17:12.271
Yan is old enough

17:12.311 --> 17:13.632
to start elementary school,

17:14.912 --> 17:16.471
and she must start studying.

17:17.231 --> 17:18.991
You must find her

17:19.031 --> 17:20.311
a primary school in the county.

17:21.031 --> 17:21.912
All these years,

17:22.672 --> 17:23.832
as parents,

17:24.352 --> 17:25.471
you've never fulfilled

17:25.551 --> 17:26.592
your responsibilities.

17:28.952 --> 17:31.832
But regarding the school enrollment,

17:32.311 --> 17:33.071
both of you must

17:33.112 --> 17:34.271
make every effort

17:34.791 --> 17:36.432
to make it right.

17:36.832 --> 17:38.112
Right, Mom.

17:38.751 --> 17:39.672
We came here

17:39.872 --> 17:42.352
to take Yan back
for attending the school.

17:42.672 --> 17:43.632
All these years,

17:44.231 --> 17:45.751
you've been raising her alone,

17:46.592 --> 17:47.912
and it's been hard.

17:48.112 --> 17:48.751
Enough!

17:48.791 --> 17:49.991
Save your sweet talk.

17:50.271 --> 17:51.071
Do you even know

17:51.672 --> 17:52.471
what Yan tells

17:52.511 --> 17:53.192
the neighborhood

17:53.352 --> 17:54.352
and kids?

17:55.471 --> 17:56.592
She says her parents

17:56.952 --> 17:57.751
are abroad.

17:58.112 --> 17:59.471
How did such a young child

17:59.592 --> 18:01.231
learn to lie?

18:03.231 --> 18:04.791
After having Lin,

18:04.832 --> 18:06.751
you insisted on trying for a boy.

18:07.271 --> 18:08.352
You knew perfectly well

18:08.632 --> 18:09.991
Yazhen has poor health.

18:10.551 --> 18:11.152
These years

18:11.791 --> 18:13.592
her health is completely ruined.

18:14.872 --> 18:16.192
Now you've got a girl,

18:16.311 --> 18:17.511
with congenital heart disease,

18:17.952 --> 18:19.432
and you don't like her.

18:19.632 --> 18:20.791
Won't you even

18:20.832 --> 18:21.632
save her life?

18:22.112 --> 18:23.231
As parents,

18:23.471 --> 18:25.271
don't you feel any guilt?

18:28.231 --> 18:28.672
Mom.

18:29.912 --> 18:30.392
Mom.

18:30.432 --> 18:31.751
We know we were wrong.

18:32.592 --> 18:33.952
We will treat Yan well

18:33.991 --> 18:34.991
and make it up for her

18:35.872 --> 18:37.872
after taking her back.

18:37.991 --> 18:38.511
Mom.

18:47.672 --> 18:48.392
Be careful.

18:49.511 --> 18:49.991
Alright.

18:50.071 --> 18:50.592
We're home.

18:50.751 --> 18:51.912
Come in.

18:53.392 --> 18:54.912
This is Mom and Dad's home.

18:55.112 --> 18:56.511
From now on, it's yours too.

18:57.271 --> 18:57.952
From today on,

18:57.991 --> 18:58.791
share this room

18:58.832 --> 18:59.791
with your elder sister.

18:59.991 --> 19:00.632
Okay?

19:01.192 --> 19:02.231
I will bring in

19:02.271 --> 19:03.071
your luggage.

19:07.352 --> 19:08.751
I packed these pretty clothes

19:08.791 --> 19:10.071
for you.

19:11.432 --> 19:12.672
At Mom and Dad's place,

19:12.952 --> 19:15.031
be sensible and obedient.

19:16.392 --> 19:17.471
Do things yourself

19:17.511 --> 19:18.592
whenever possible.

19:19.711 --> 19:21.311
I also packed these things you like

19:21.471 --> 19:22.791
for you.

19:26.231 --> 19:27.311
At mealtimes,

19:27.632 --> 19:29.071
don't fight with your sister.

19:30.392 --> 19:30.952
Understand?

19:33.872 --> 19:35.551
I will miss you.

19:46.672 --> 19:47.392
Take a look.

19:48.071 --> 19:49.231
This is your home now.

19:52.031 --> 19:53.071
Alright, it's late.

19:53.432 --> 19:54.751
Let's bathe and sleep.

19:54.791 --> 19:55.912
Come on, I will bathe you.

19:56.471 --> 19:58.352
Mom, I can bathe myself.

20:01.471 --> 20:01.872
Alright.

20:02.632 --> 20:03.872
You can bathe yourself.

20:04.231 --> 20:04.832
Then,

20:04.952 --> 20:05.872
take off the clothes

20:05.912 --> 20:07.031
and I will wash them. Okay?

20:07.551 --> 20:09.711
Mom, I can wash my clothes.

21:03.311 --> 21:04.711
Why is the smell of gas so strong?

21:14.311 --> 21:14.791
Lin!

21:15.991 --> 21:16.471
Lin!

21:18.872 --> 21:19.352
Lin!

21:27.952 --> 21:29.751
Wake up! Don't scare me!

21:29.791 --> 21:30.192
What?

21:30.192 --> 21:30.832
Help!

21:31.071 --> 21:31.872
Help! Help!

21:32.352 --> 21:33.071
What's going on?

21:33.071 --> 21:33.952
Gas poisoning!

21:34.152 --> 21:35.432
Lin, wake up!

21:35.672 --> 21:36.112
Lin!

21:36.751 --> 21:37.592
Call the ambulance!

21:37.592 --> 21:38.791
Okay, stay calm.

21:38.952 --> 21:39.392
Lin!

21:39.392 --> 21:40.751
Wake up! Wake up!

21:40.872 --> 21:42.311
Don't scare me.

21:42.311 --> 21:42.791
Lin.

21:43.271 --> 21:44.751
Wake up, wake up. Lin!

21:45.271 --> 21:45.751
Lin!

21:46.031 --> 21:46.991
What's going on?

21:47.311 --> 21:47.791
Qiao?

21:47.832 --> 21:48.592
Lin has poisoned...

21:49.231 --> 21:50.192
Where have you been?

21:50.231 --> 21:51.672
You didn't turn off the gas.

21:51.791 --> 21:52.392
Lin!

21:52.592 --> 21:53.551
Lin, are you okay?

21:53.592 --> 21:54.271
Stop shouting!

21:54.271 --> 21:56.071
Go call an ambulance!

21:57.352 --> 21:57.872
Qiao!

21:58.432 --> 21:59.031
Where's Yan?

22:02.912 --> 22:03.432
Yan!

22:04.311 --> 22:05.271
Another one?

22:05.592 --> 22:06.152
Yan!

22:07.311 --> 22:07.872
Help out!

22:09.872 --> 22:10.991
It is all my fault.

22:11.311 --> 22:12.511
I'm so sorry.

22:12.672 --> 22:13.511
My daughter.

22:15.592 --> 22:16.031
Here.

22:17.231 --> 22:17.952
Have a banana.

22:18.551 --> 22:19.711
Let Dad feed you.

22:20.751 --> 22:21.632
Open your mouth.

22:22.271 --> 22:24.071
One more bite. A big bite.

22:24.112 --> 22:24.672
Come on.

22:28.511 --> 22:29.071
Good girl.

22:29.511 --> 22:30.551
I will make you

22:30.592 --> 22:31.872
your favorite braised pork.

22:32.192 --> 22:32.711
Okay?

22:36.272 --> 22:38.640
(Qiao Yan: 12 years old,
Qiao Lin: 14 years old)

22:47.352 --> 22:47.872
Yan!

22:48.152 --> 22:48.952
Perfect timing.

22:49.152 --> 22:50.551
Lin got into a fight.

22:50.711 --> 22:51.711
We need to go there.

22:52.031 --> 22:53.152
You can have instant noodles.

22:53.952 --> 22:55.071
Qiao, hurry up!

22:57.311 --> 23:00.991
(Happy birthday)
â™ªHappy birthday to youâ™ª

23:01.872 --> 23:05.432
â™ªHappy birthday to youâ™ª

23:06.152 --> 23:09.112
â™ªHappy birthdayâ™ª

23:14.112 --> 23:15.751
Yan? Is that you?

23:16.311 --> 23:17.471
Happy birthday.

23:17.912 --> 23:19.071
Grandma.

23:22.711 --> 23:24.392
Alright, don't cry.

23:24.991 --> 23:25.751
Come to my place.

23:25.991 --> 23:27.271
I'll make you delicious food.

23:27.872 --> 23:28.551
Okay?

23:37.952 --> 23:38.711
You are

23:39.112 --> 23:40.872
always getting into fights.

23:41.271 --> 23:42.711
You even fought with a boy!

23:45.432 --> 23:46.471
That's your classmate.

23:46.511 --> 23:47.872
What if you hurt him?

23:48.672 --> 23:49.112
See?

23:49.231 --> 23:49.952
The teacher

23:49.991 --> 23:50.912
always calls us in

23:51.432 --> 23:52.311
to apologize.

23:52.352 --> 23:52.952
Keep quiet.

23:53.751 --> 23:54.311
She's asleep.

23:55.672 --> 23:56.551
Compensate them,

23:56.952 --> 23:58.112
treat them meals,

23:58.912 --> 23:59.952
(Mom, Dad, I'm going to bed.)
and apologize!

23:59.952 --> 24:00.976
(I've eaten. Don't worry.)

24:01.152 --> 24:01.791
See?

24:02.271 --> 24:03.192
Yan is well-behaved.

24:03.471 --> 24:03.991
But you

24:04.071 --> 24:05.432
spend all day fighting,

24:05.551 --> 24:06.711
not giving us a break.

24:06.872 --> 24:08.271
Mom, I'm hungry.

24:08.471 --> 24:09.071
Alright.

24:09.112 --> 24:09.872
You're hungry.

24:10.071 --> 24:11.311
We're busy apologizing,

24:11.471 --> 24:12.392
and haven't eaten.

24:12.791 --> 24:13.231
Here.

24:13.392 --> 24:14.311
I'll reheat this.

24:15.031 --> 24:15.471
Come here.

24:15.551 --> 24:16.711
What do you want? Noodles?

24:16.751 --> 24:17.271
Okay.

24:17.471 --> 24:17.991
I'm hungry.

24:17.991 --> 24:18.471
Take a bath.

24:18.471 --> 24:18.791
Mom.

24:18.912 --> 24:19.711
Eat after your bath.

24:19.751 --> 24:20.672
I'm hungry.

24:24.592 --> 24:25.231
Bathe yourself.

24:26.912 --> 24:28.432
I need to wash these clothes.

24:28.471 --> 24:29.632
You need them tomorrow.

24:34.231 --> 24:35.112
Wrap yourself up.

24:35.152 --> 24:35.991
Don't catch a cold.

24:45.751 --> 24:47.152
(Qiao Yan: 18 years old)
Qiao Yan obtained great scores

24:47.271 --> 24:48.392
(Qiao Lin: 20 years old)
in recent mock exams.

24:48.592 --> 24:50.031
She's ranked top 30 in her grade.

24:50.551 --> 24:52.271
She can get into a top college
in Jingzhou.

24:53.031 --> 24:54.432
As for the major,

24:54.551 --> 24:55.071
you should

24:55.071 --> 24:56.231
discuss it with her,

24:56.632 --> 24:57.751
and guide her.

25:01.912 --> 25:03.311
She can obtain

25:03.352 --> 25:04.352
such outstanding results,

25:04.751 --> 25:07.192
thanks to your dedicated guidance.

25:08.551 --> 25:11.912
But, she won't attend
the college entrance exam.

25:12.352 --> 25:13.912
We have other plans for her.

25:14.592 --> 25:15.912
What?

25:17.392 --> 25:18.751
Given her academic performance,

25:19.511 --> 25:20.751
it would be a pity.

25:21.551 --> 25:22.112
Have you

25:22.352 --> 25:23.471
discussed this with her?

25:24.192 --> 25:25.112
What does she think?

25:26.751 --> 25:28.432
A child can't understand

25:28.471 --> 25:29.551
our family's hardships.

25:30.832 --> 25:31.632
I can decide this

25:32.231 --> 25:32.991
for her.

25:35.271 --> 25:36.991
Why forbid me from attending the exam?

25:39.471 --> 25:40.832
I'm talking with your teacher.

25:40.952 --> 25:41.551
Why forbid me

25:41.592 --> 25:43.152
from attending the exam?

25:47.271 --> 25:48.271
Because I'm your dad!

25:48.751 --> 25:50.071
I'm the head of our family!

25:53.511 --> 25:54.071
Sorry, Miss.

25:54.112 --> 25:54.551
Sorry

25:54.551 --> 25:55.511
for the embarrassment.

25:56.952 --> 25:58.152
This decision is final.

25:58.872 --> 25:59.432
Go home.

26:06.592 --> 26:08.791
Why won't you let me attend the college?

26:08.832 --> 26:09.511
Dad!

26:10.592 --> 26:13.511
Why won't you let me attend the college?

26:17.751 --> 26:19.192
Dad, wait for me!

26:19.511 --> 26:20.751
Wait!

26:22.711 --> 26:24.432
Wait!

26:24.632 --> 26:26.511
Wait for me!

26:31.271 --> 26:32.711
Why?

26:32.872 --> 26:33.791
Why?

26:33.952 --> 26:35.192
Why?

26:35.952 --> 26:36.912
Why?

26:37.912 --> 26:39.152
Because we're poor.

26:39.592 --> 26:40.952
Because the expenses

26:41.031 --> 26:41.872
for college are high,

26:42.112 --> 26:42.991
and we can't support

26:42.991 --> 26:44.112
two college students.

26:44.471 --> 26:45.432
So we choose

26:45.471 --> 26:47.071
to let Lin go to college.

26:48.832 --> 26:50.231
Dad, what about me?

26:52.392 --> 26:53.711
What about me?

26:56.912 --> 26:58.271
After you finish high school,

26:59.791 --> 27:01.672
we'll help you find a job.

27:02.392 --> 27:04.392
This way, you can stay with us.

27:04.432 --> 27:06.672
And we can take care of you.

27:07.952 --> 27:08.471
Wait.

27:09.192 --> 27:09.672
I...

27:10.392 --> 27:11.632
I want to know why...

27:14.231 --> 27:16.311
Why have you always been

27:16.352 --> 27:17.991
so biased all the time?

27:21.952 --> 27:25.471
Why does Qiao Lin
get all the good things?

27:26.471 --> 27:27.271
Am I...

27:27.311 --> 27:29.632
Am I not your biological child?

27:31.791 --> 27:34.711
Why do you always make me feel

27:34.791 --> 27:37.192
that you don't love me?

27:40.592 --> 27:43.031
I thought if I kept lying to myself

27:43.231 --> 27:45.471
and kept studying hard,

27:45.511 --> 27:46.632
behaving well,

27:46.672 --> 27:47.952
and listening to you,

27:48.031 --> 27:50.152
you'd finally love me.

27:51.592 --> 27:55.551
Why can't I keep lying to myself now?

27:55.632 --> 27:55.991
What...

27:57.352 --> 27:59.432
What have I ever wronged you?

27:59.872 --> 28:00.952
We've provided you

28:01.311 --> 28:03.392
everything you needed,

28:04.071 --> 28:06.112
so why can't you be considerate?

28:06.192 --> 28:07.991
You forbid me from attending the college

28:08.071 --> 28:10.311
without consulting me!

28:11.832 --> 28:13.711
What you're doing is theft!

28:14.432 --> 28:15.872
What you're doing is robbery!

28:15.872 --> 28:17.751
How dare you speak
to your dad like this!

28:18.112 --> 28:19.152
So outrageous!

28:19.952 --> 28:22.912
You will only be an ungrateful child

28:23.031 --> 28:24.352
even with a college degree!

28:25.432 --> 28:27.592
How horrible am I?

28:31.432 --> 28:34.311
What terrible thing have I done?

28:36.231 --> 28:37.832
I don't understand.

28:40.551 --> 28:41.592
I don't understand

28:41.672 --> 28:45.711
why you have to prove

28:45.952 --> 28:48.551
how much you don't love me.

28:48.952 --> 28:50.112
Why?

28:50.392 --> 28:52.912
Why do I have to be your daughter?

30:01.832 --> 30:02.751
Grandma.

30:05.751 --> 30:06.551
Grandma.

30:06.672 --> 30:07.471
Coming.

30:10.311 --> 30:10.991
Yan.

30:11.872 --> 30:12.271
You...

30:13.031 --> 30:13.592
Grandma.

30:17.511 --> 30:18.352
I know

30:18.832 --> 30:19.952
you've been wronged.

30:23.192 --> 30:25.952
Look, you're all wet.

30:59.024 --> 31:00.929
(Incoming call from Shen Haoming)

31:08.912 --> 31:09.751
Hello, Haoming.

31:10.632 --> 31:14.192
- What are you doing?
- I'm on my way home.

31:15.352 --> 31:17.632
Can you come to my studio?

31:18.832 --> 31:19.471
Now?

31:20.152 --> 31:20.551
Yes.

31:20.872 --> 31:21.271
Hurry.

31:21.751 --> 31:22.231
Okay.

31:27.271 --> 31:28.511
Change the address, please.

31:37.952 --> 31:38.511
What's wrong?

31:47.031 --> 31:48.192
A flower stalk has grown?

31:52.432 --> 31:53.711
This plant is sixty years old.

31:55.112 --> 31:56.071
I think

31:56.511 --> 31:57.432
tonight

31:57.592 --> 31:58.511
it will bloom.

32:00.432 --> 32:02.031
If it does bloom,

32:03.112 --> 32:04.832
this will undoubtedly be

32:04.872 --> 32:05.991
its most glorious moment.

32:06.952 --> 32:08.551
I want to witness this with you.

32:14.672 --> 32:16.672
I remember you once mentioned

32:17.672 --> 32:21.031
the agave only blooms
once in its lifetime.

32:22.912 --> 32:25.192
So after blooming,

32:26.832 --> 32:27.632
it will die.

32:31.592 --> 32:32.592
After blooming,

32:34.352 --> 32:36.031
it will wither rapidly

32:37.672 --> 32:38.592
and drain

32:39.791 --> 32:40.432
until

32:41.112 --> 32:41.872
returning to dust.

32:43.832 --> 32:45.311
It has exhausted all the nutrients

32:45.432 --> 32:46.872
throughout its life

32:48.672 --> 32:49.832
and endured hardship

32:51.632 --> 32:53.551
just for this moment to bloom.

32:55.471 --> 32:56.311
This is truly

32:56.311 --> 32:57.311
its swan song.

33:05.192 --> 33:05.711
What's wrong?

33:08.031 --> 33:09.231
I just feel

33:11.112 --> 33:12.392
it is pitiful.

33:14.832 --> 33:16.952
Its whole life
is spent battling hardships,

33:16.991 --> 33:17.952
and growing tenaciously,

33:18.471 --> 33:20.031
just for a single moment to bloom.

33:23.751 --> 33:25.071
Because it has no choice.

33:28.471 --> 33:29.392
It must

33:29.432 --> 33:30.632
stay stronger,

33:30.832 --> 33:31.551
work harder,

33:32.231 --> 33:33.152
and endure more

33:34.952 --> 33:36.071
than others to achieve

33:36.152 --> 33:37.112
their beautiful endings.

33:38.031 --> 33:39.192
Waiting for long

33:40.071 --> 33:41.912
and suffering the torment

33:42.271 --> 33:43.791
are all the price it pays.

33:56.711 --> 33:58.192
Blossoming, fruiting,

34:00.071 --> 34:01.672
aging, and being reborn

34:02.952 --> 34:03.952
happen in cycles.

34:04.711 --> 34:05.751
This is the law of nature.

34:07.551 --> 34:09.591
But when each agave

34:09.631 --> 34:10.671
blooms,

34:11.432 --> 34:12.111
its pollen

34:12.191 --> 34:13.912
scatters around,

34:15.151 --> 34:16.712
and meets another agave.

34:18.232 --> 34:19.631
They cross-pollinate

34:19.832 --> 34:21.752
and produce more seeds.

34:23.031 --> 34:24.031
These seeds

34:24.671 --> 34:25.511
become

34:25.511 --> 34:26.432
their legacy

34:26.872 --> 34:27.952
in this world,

34:28.872 --> 34:30.031
just like humans.

34:32.151 --> 34:32.792
Meeting,

34:33.471 --> 34:34.111
loving,

34:35.432 --> 34:36.912
marrying, and having children.

34:38.511 --> 34:39.832
A century later,

34:41.272 --> 34:41.952
though the people

34:41.991 --> 34:42.991
may be gone,

34:44.511 --> 34:46.272
their love endures.

34:52.191 --> 34:54.191
When two agaves meet,

34:55.712 --> 34:56.872
they do everything

34:59.392 --> 35:00.551
for each other,

35:01.232 --> 35:02.712
even at the cost of their lives.

35:03.712 --> 35:04.912
Because they know

35:05.232 --> 35:05.952
their love

35:07.392 --> 35:07.912
is worth it.

35:08.792 --> 35:09.872
They never regret it.

35:10.671 --> 35:11.591
Just like you and me.

35:12.312 --> 35:13.272
Meeting you

35:15.752 --> 35:16.872
and being with you.

35:18.752 --> 35:19.631
No matter what price

35:19.671 --> 35:20.671
I must pay,

35:23.591 --> 35:24.272
I will never

35:26.471 --> 35:27.471
regret it.

35:30.792 --> 35:31.272
And you?

35:33.551 --> 35:34.752
Think it carefully.

35:36.352 --> 35:37.912
I do regret...

35:43.511 --> 35:44.912
I regret getting married next month.

